com.cyc.kb

Interface Symbol

  • All Superinterfaces:
    KBObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SymbolImpl

    public interface Symbol
extends KBObject
    The interface for symbols of the SubL language. Symbols are occasionally referenced in CycL assertions, most notably those that denote SubL functions that test for membership in a collection or perform simple functions like string manipulation or arithmetic.
